==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Chosen
<hw>Cho"sen</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>p. p.</pos> <mord>of
<er>Choose</er></mord>. <def>Selected from a number; picked out;
choice.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Seven hundred <qex>chosen</qex> men left-handed.</q>
<rj><qau>Judg. xx. 16.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Chosen</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Chosen
<hw>Cho"sen</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that which is the
object of choice or special favor.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Chou</ent>⟦br⟧
